"    .  .  .  .  .  .  .  .  .  .  .  .   "
"   .  .  _  .  _  .  .  .|`|  .  .  .    "
"    .  o`.\,=./.`o .  . _|_|_  .  .  .   "
"   .  .  :(o o):  .  .  (o)o) .  .  .    "
"   ---ooO-(._.)-Ooo-ooO-(._.)-Ooo---     "
"    ╔═╗╦╔═╗╦  ╔═╗╔╗╔╔═╗╔╦╗╔═╗╔═╗╔╗╔      "
"    ║  ║║ ║║  ╠═╣║║║╚═╗ ║ ║╣ ║╣ ║║║      "
"    ╚═╝╩╚═╝╩═╝╩ ╩╝╚╝╚═╝ ╩ ╚═╝╚═╝╝╚╝`s    "
"           vimplugins file               "
